<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="CH1a0930-en-789ddc31" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>PhD</title><editor role="translator">Tsao Ding-ren</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>PhD</title>University Michigan International, 1985</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#CH1a0930"><title xml:lang="och">鬼谷子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="en">English</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#Isabelle">Initially created: <date>2024-07-29T21:38:42.186+09:00</date> by Isabelle</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="CH1a0930-start"><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:42:44.359+09:00">If we examine the past, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:43:18.571+09:00">we find that sages who have lived between heaven and earth</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:43:52.458+09:00">have always been ahead of ordinary beings.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:45:13.824+09:00">They observed the stirring and ceasing of yin and yang and named things according to their natures.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:45:52.475+09:00">They know the passages to survival or perdition.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:46:45.924+09:00">They can calculate the initiation and termination of all events.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:47:10.295+09:00">They understand the principles of the human mind.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:48:16.649+09:00">They are perceptive of the slightest signals of change</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:48:47.066+09:00">and can guard the passages (to survival or perdition). </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:51:48.42+09:00">Therefore, from antiquity till now, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:51:42.678+09:00">the Way of all sages under heaven</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-29T21:51:18.215+09:00">has been the same. </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T15:59:04.425+09:00">Of the infinite changes,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T15:59:14.258+09:00">each has its own inclinations.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:01:03.723+09:00">It is either yin or yang,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:01:54.92+09:00">it is either tender or hard,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:05:40.51+09:00">it is either open or closed,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:06:18.605+09:00">it is either relaxed or tense.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:10:20.273+09:00">Because of these, a sage can guard a passage, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:11:04.849+09:00">evaluate priorities, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:12:24.685+09:00">gauge relative strengths and capabilities,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:14:50.705+09:00">and compare the amount of skills.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:17:34.978+09:00">[People's character vary.] Some are worthy, some unworthy; some are wise, some dull; some are brave, some timid; and there are degrees of kindness and morality.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:21:50.649+09:00">Accordingly, they may be "opened up" (pai) </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:21:56.497+09:00">or "closed down" (ho);</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:22:27.142+09:00">they may be pushed forward</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:22:32.427+09:00">or held back.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:23:55.574+09:00">They may be despised</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:24:16.976+09:00">or honored.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:26:29.177+09:00">All may be shepherded without any overt intervention.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:27:15.051+09:00">To determine a person's strengths and weaknesses,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:27:47.174+09:00">together with his real and unreal qualities,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:30:36.686+09:00">I should follow to detect his intentions and will.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:33:12.842+09:00">Slightly rejecting what he says,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:35:06.001+09:00">I prod him to respond </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:35:11.342+09:00">in order to find the truth.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:38:42.985+09:00">When doing so, it is important to get his main idea.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:39:49.756+09:00">If I keep silent, so that he will open up,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:10:57.42+09:00">I may thus gain advantage [in approaching him].</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:05:51.376+09:00">Either I open and reveal myself </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:05:22.193+09:00">or I close and conceal myself.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:52:50.871+09:00">I open and reveal myself</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:07:49.516+09:00">[In deciding] to talk or not to talk,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T16:53:25.672+09:00">to show that our feelings are identical.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:04:58.531+09:00">I close and keep silent,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:04:53.167+09:00">because there are differences in our true feelings.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:08:54.515+09:00">I should carefully examine and understand his plans</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:09:08.577+09:00">to trace the source of agreement or disagreement.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:12:48.743+09:00">[In deciding] whether to disagree or agree,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-07-31T17:14:31.858+09:00">the first thing to do is to follow his intentions.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:09:52.655+09:00">When I wish to prod him, I should be all inclusive.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:11:57.278+09:00">When I wish to be silent, I should be secretive.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:12:32.911+09:00">In being secretive, I should be subtle</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:13:13.569+09:00">and follow the Way.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:15:30.779+09:00">To prod (pai) is to anticipate his feelings.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:19:02.362+09:00"> To keep silence (ho) is to [let him speak so that I can] bind his sincerity.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:21:58.786+09:00">In all cases, after perceiving whether he is light or heavy on the scale</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:22:30.632+09:00">and figuring out how to compensate the imbalance,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:25:23.693+09:00">the sage proceeds to make plans with him in mind.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:29:23.235+09:00">If he does not pass evaluation, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:29:41.974+09:00">the sage proceeds to make plans despite of him.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:37:29.519+09:00">Therefore prodding (pai) </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:38:53.072+09:00">can result in either standing out </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:38:56.202+09:00">or being contained.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:39:55.951+09:00">Silence (ho) can result in either adoption</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:39:58.873+09:00">or rejection.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:41:45.519+09:00">Opening and Closing (pai and ho) is the Way of heaven and earth.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:57:06.908+09:00">They change the balance of yin and yang,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:57:53.506+09:00">the four seasons open and close,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T16:59:10.113+09:00">thus transforming the vertical and horizontal relationship of all things. </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T17:00:45.324+09:00">All reflection (fan) and responses (fu) proceed from these. </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-3a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:22:01.66+09:00"/><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:17:43.712+09:00">Since opening (pai) and closing (ho) are the great transforming movements of the Way</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:17:18.39+09:00">and changing force in persuasion, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:23:24.076+09:00">one must make careful investigation of them. The great decrees of good and bad fortune are bound to them.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:24:22.148+09:00">The mouth is the doorway of the heart.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:24:19.773+09:00">The heart is the master of the spirit.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:40:41.792+09:00">Through this doorway, one's will, intentions, delights, desires, thoughts, worries, wisdoms and plans </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:40:44.803+09:00">go in and out.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:41:14.087+09:00">This doorway, therefore, should be carefully guarded </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:41:16.02+09:00">and moderated by [the uses of] pai-ho.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:37:45.872+09:00">and is yang.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:36:13.304+09:00">is speaking,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:36:56.512+09:00">Pai is "to open",</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:38:06.89+09:00">Ho is "to close",</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:38:14.439+09:00"> is silence, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:38:17.769+09:00">and is yin.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:42:38.426+09:00">When yin and yang are balances harmoniously,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:43:06.08+09:00">the beginning and end are justified.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:48:52.086+09:00">Speech which concerns longevity, happiness, prosperity, honor, reputation, likes, benefits, satisfactions, delights is yang,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:46:41.145+09:00">and is the beginning.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:50:16.057+09:00">[And by the same token,] speech which concerns death, worries, poverty, insults, abandonments, losses, disappointments, damages, punishments, indictments is yin, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:50:28.656+09:00">and is the end.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:53:34.374+09:00">Words belonging in the yang category</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:54:38.047+09:00">are called "the beginning" </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:55:19.319+09:00">because the good is spoken so that events can begin.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:56:30.708+09:00">Words belonging to the yin category</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:56:40.266+09:00">are called "the end"</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-4a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:57:08.02+09:00">because the bad is spoken so that plans can be terminated.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:58:06.151+09:00">The Way of opening and closing </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:58:16.719+09:00">is to be used in accordance with yin and yang.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:59:06.309+09:00">When speaking with those who are yang, use lofty and sublime language.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T18:59:43.156+09:00">When speaking with those who are yin, use petty and restricted language.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:02:37.229+09:00">Use the base to deal with the petty</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:02:49.288+09:00">and use the sublime to deal with the great.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:03:16.862+09:00">To speak from these principles,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:03:33.15+09:00">there is nothing which cannot be brought out,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:03:51.48+09:00">nothing which cannot be penetrated</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:04:13.589+09:00">and nothing which is impossible.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:04:59.159+09:00">One may use them to persuade ordinary people,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:05:31.106+09:00">families,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:05:57.934+09:00">even the state</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:05:45.753+09:00">and the whole realm.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:06:53.026+09:00">Nothing is too small when using the petty.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:07:29.278+09:00">Nothing is too big when using the great.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:08:58.809+09:00">Whether to increase or diminish, to reject or to accept, to leave or to return,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:09:58.681+09:00">in all cases, matters are to be guided by yin-yang.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:10:48.445+09:00">When yang moves, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:11:04.011+09:00">yin stops and becomes concealed.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:19:35.596+09:00">When yang comes out, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:20:48.401+09:00">yin hides and retires. </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:21:14.104+09:00">Yang eventually ends up in yin,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:21:16.602+09:00">yin ultimately returns to yang.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:22:28.865+09:00">When one moves with yang, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:22:30.823+09:00">virtue is generated.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:23:07.772+09:00">When one keeps silence with yin,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:23:33.068+09:00">forms are accomplished.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:24:21.193+09:00">Starting from yang to seek yin</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:24:10.851+09:00">is to enfold with virtue.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:25:06.659+09:00">Starting from yin to seek yang</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:25:12.324+09:00">is to exert force.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:25:54.377+09:00">The mutual seeking of yin and yang</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:26:07.788+09:00">comes from the use of pai and ho.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:27:46.915+09:00">This is the yin-yang way of heaven and earth,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:28:11.024+09:00">and is the method of persuasion.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:29:00.335+09:00">As it precedes all things and events in the universe, </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0930_CHANT_001-5a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#Isabelle" modified="2024-08-01T19:29:37.966+09:00">it can be called the doorway of heaven and earth.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>